Davido and his fiancee Chioma Avril are having the best time of their lives after showing off photos while on vacation in Dubai. Recall that Chioma recently gave birth to the singer’s son and he decided to give her a treat by taking her to Dubai to have fun. The singer took to his social media page to show off photos of the duo in Dubai dressed in Arabian outfit. He captioned it: “Desert Day with the Wife 😍” Desert Day with the Wife 😍 A post shared by  Davido Adeleke (@davidoofficial) on Feb 6, 2020 at 4:03am PST